page.text: Re: Frederick/Carroll County Renewable Waste-to-Energy Facility (FCCRWTE)
Environmental Consulting & Technology, Inc., on behalf of Northeast Maryland Waste
Disposal Authority and Wheelabrator Technologies, Inc., is submitting the enclosed two
copies of the amended Refuse Disposal Permit application for FCCRWTE. The amended
application incorporates the additional information requested by the Maryland Depart-
ment of the Environment in their correspondence dated August 5, 2011, and January 10,
2012. Additional copies may be provided at your request.
Questions regarding this amended application should be directed to Mr. Jim Connolly,
Senior Manager, Environmental Permitting, Wheelabrator Technologies, Inc., at
cc. A. Kays, Northeast Maryland Waste Disposal Authority
